- **Conventional Commits**: `feat|fix|refactor|build|ci|chore|docs|style|perf|test`
- **File limit**: ~500 LOC
- **Plans dir**: `docs/plans/` (active) / `docs/plans/complete/` (done)
- **Design docs**: `docs/design-docs/`
- **Product specs**: `docs/product-specs/`
